00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:23,010
You fainted in the outpatient clinic.

564
00:29:23,010 --> 00:29:24,810
We did an MRI of your brain.

565
00:29:25,050 --> 00:29:27,010
We found a tumor growing

566
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,440
on your brain stem.

567
00:29:28,690 --> 00:29:29,720
Based on my experience,

568
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:31,570
it's likely to be malignant.

569
00:29:39,650 --> 00:29:40,890
How long do I have?

570
00:29:42,650 --> 00:29:43,720
Depends on the treatment plan.

571
00:29:45,770 --> 00:29:46,770
Can you save me?

572
00:29:47,810 --> 00:29:48,890
I can't make any promise,

573
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,720
but I will do my best.

574
00:29:53,410 --> 00:29:54,290
I trust you,

575
00:29:54,690 --> 00:29:55,410
Dr. Ning.

576
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,440
We might need

577
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,810
to run some other tests on you later.

578
00:30:00,810 --> 00:30:01,720
Get some rest.

579
00:30:06,930 --> 00:30:08,010
My name is Ruan Liuzheng.

580
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:10,290
Deputy Manager Ning
put me in charge of your case.

581
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:11,320
If you need anything,

582
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:13,010
ring that bell behind you.

583
00:30:13,010 --> 00:30:13,810
It's behind you.

584
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:22,480
Do you think he's telling the truth?

585
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,440
About what?

586
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,440
About not having any family.

587
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:26,720
How would I know?

588
00:30:28,050 --> 00:30:30,010
Do you think he said that

589
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:30,960
because he didn't want
to worry his family?

590
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,480
Can you not fuss over these things?

591
00:30:33,080 --> 00:30:34,840
Can't you have some empathy
for your patients?

592
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,650
Can your empathy

593
00:30:35,650 --> 00:30:36,960
remove his tumor?

594
00:30:39,830 --> 00:30:45,190
(Beiya Hospital)

595
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:52,840
Mr. Ning.

596
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,170
I think you got in the wrong car.

597
00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:57,080
Didn't you promise Ning Xiang

598
00:30:57,080 --> 00:30:58,810
you would come to my place
to see him a few days ago?

599
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:02,050
I think I did.

600
00:31:02,770 --> 00:31:03,440
Let's go.

601
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,530
Slow down.

602
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:51,840
Is he asleep?

603
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:53,050
Yes.

604
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:55,410
Leave the dishes.

605
00:31:55,410 --> 00:31:56,360
I'll wash them later.

606
00:31:57,050 --> 00:31:58,360
I wasn't planning on cleaning them.

607
00:31:59,080 --> 00:31:59,810
Mr. Ning,

608
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:02,360
you've been on your laptop all night,

609
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:04,170
ordering me to do this and that.

610
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,960
Do you actually take me for the nanny?

611
00:32:07,930 --> 00:32:09,600
Of course not.

612
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:11,120
Everyone has times when they're busy.

613
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,960
I'm not goofing around. I'm working.

614
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:13,770
Besides,

615
00:32:13,770 --> 00:32:15,570
the boy likes your cooking.

616
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,320
He wants you to play with him.

617
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,410
What can I do?

618
00:32:19,890 --> 00:32:21,840
Fine. That's my fault.

619
00:32:22,290 --> 00:32:23,770
When are you going to find him a mother?

620
00:32:24,120 --> 00:32:25,690
I'll hurry up.

621
00:32:25,810 --> 00:32:27,720
But the problem now is

622
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,360
even if I do find him a mother,

623
00:32:29,360 --> 00:32:30,720
he'll regard her as a stepmother.

624
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,240
I don't even know if he'll accept her.

625
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:33,930
Do you know what this is?

626
00:32:34,290 --> 00:32:36,010
Chain reaction.

627
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:37,170
Your showing-up

628
00:32:37,170 --> 00:32:38,810
complicated things.

629
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,600
Fine. My bad.

630
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:41,810
I'm leaving.

631
00:32:42,840 --> 00:32:43,890
I won't see you off.

632
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,440
(Zhiqian)

633
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:49,120
(Zhiqian)

634
00:32:50,410 --> 00:32:51,320
Ning Zhiqian!

635
00:32:52,810 --> 00:32:53,530
Who is it?

636
00:32:54,530 --> 00:32:55,720
(I'm Xiao'er!)

637
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,200
It's my brother.
Do you want to say hello?

638
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:02,200
Open the door, Zhiqian!

639
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,570
Mom.

640
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,010
Took you long enough.
Are you hiding a lover?

641
00:33:29,010 --> 00:33:29,770
Hold this.

642
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:31,240
I need to use the toilet!

643
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:52,690
Is Ning Xiang asleep?

644
00:33:52,690 --> 00:33:53,840
I haven't seen him in a while.

645
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,480
I'll check on him.

646
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,410
He is asleep.

647
00:33:55,410 --> 00:33:56,960
Don't go inside. Don't wake him up.

648
00:33:58,530 --> 00:33:59,440
Ning Xiang?

649
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:00,690
Uncle?

650
00:34:00,690 --> 00:34:02,010
I brought you gifts.

651
00:34:02,050 --> 00:34:03,930
Play with them when you wake up.

652
00:34:05,010 --> 00:34:05,650
Dad...

653
00:34:05,770 --> 00:34:06,440
No talking.

654
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,360
Go back to sleep.

655
00:34:08,090 --> 00:34:09,160
See? You woke him up.

656
00:34:09,610 --> 00:34:10,200
Go back to sleep.

657
00:34:10,200 --> 00:34:11,160
Go to sleep.

658
00:34:14,130 --> 00:34:15,400
It took a long time to put him to bed.

659
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,880
Why are you here so late at night?

660
00:34:18,240 --> 00:34:19,130
I bought these

661
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:20,610
just for you and your boy

662
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:21,610
when I was on business trip
in Northeast China.

663
00:34:22,330 --> 00:34:23,050
Thank you.

664
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:24,440
Hey, I came to visit for once.

665
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:25,680
Let's have a chat.

666
00:34:25,810 --> 00:34:26,330
A chat?

667
00:34:26,770 --> 00:34:28,200
What's there to chat about at this hour?

668
00:34:29,010 --> 00:34:29,880
Sit down.

669
00:34:30,160 --> 00:34:31,010
I need to talk to you about something.

670
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,570
How's the case
with you beating up a patient's family

671
00:34:33,570 --> 00:34:34,570
going?

672
00:34:35,610 --> 00:34:36,400
It's resolved.

673
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,050
Has it been settled?

674
00:34:37,090 --> 00:34:38,240
If that's the only reason you're here,

675
00:34:38,330 --> 00:34:39,850
you could've just called me.

676
00:34:40,010 --> 00:34:41,050
It's not the first time
this happens.

677
00:34:41,050 --> 00:34:42,200
Would I need to come all the way here
just because of that?

678
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:44,240
It's your sister-in-law. She woke me up

679
00:34:44,240 --> 00:34:45,200
at 3 AM last night,

680
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:46,370
and said she dreamed of your mother.

681
00:34:49,240 --> 00:34:50,810
My wife dreamed of your mother.

682
00:34:51,610 --> 00:34:52,570
She dreamed of my mother?

683
00:34:53,570 --> 00:34:55,570
She said your mother came to her dreams,

684
00:34:55,720 --> 00:34:57,810
telling her that she's worried about you

685
00:34:57,850 --> 00:34:59,680
in heaven because you have a kid
but not a wife.

686
00:34:59,850 --> 00:35:00,770
So she wanted me to ask you

687
00:35:00,810 --> 00:35:01,960
what kind of woman you like.

688
00:35:02,290 --> 00:35:03,640
You've met at least a dozen girls

689
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:05,160
over the past years.

690
00:35:05,370 --> 00:35:06,530
Is there really no one to your liking?

691
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,720
It's fine. The boy is asleep.

692
00:35:09,720 --> 00:35:10,810
Still, keep it down.

693
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:11,810
Okay.

694
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:14,240
What about Liu, the model?

695
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,920
Beautiful face. Great physique.

696
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:18,920
She is good.

697
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,200
I think she suits you.

698
00:35:20,370 --> 00:35:21,130
To heck with you.

699
00:35:21,130 --> 00:35:22,480
Can my wife compare?

700
00:35:24,050 --> 00:35:25,010
What about Wang, the rich lady?

701
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,240
We shared a meal once.

702
00:35:28,290 --> 00:35:29,240
Her palate is too strong.

703
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:30,570
I don't think we can get over
our difference in flavor preference.

704
00:35:31,330 --> 00:35:32,290
Right.

705
00:35:32,290 --> 00:35:34,240
Can't compromise on food.

706
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,200
What about Lin, the teacher?

707
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:36,960
She gets summer and winter breaks,

708
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,440
and she can even tutor Ning Xiang.

709
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,400
I thought she was good,

710
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:43,050
but Ning Xiang thought
she was too fierce and strict.

711
00:35:43,050 --> 00:35:44,130
He's intimidated by her.

712
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:45,810
You two are so fussy.

713
00:35:48,290 --> 00:35:49,010
All right.

714
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:50,960
Tell me what type of woman you like.

715
00:35:52,050 --> 00:35:53,130
Someone suitable.

716
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:54,440
What?

717
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,810
Suitable.

718
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,160
What does that even mean?

719
00:35:59,570 --> 00:36:01,200
It's like answering "anything"

720
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,090
when I ask you what you want to eat.

721
00:36:02,090 --> 00:36:03,640
I hate people like you
who can't decide what they want.

722
00:36:03,770 --> 00:36:04,640
How am I supposed

723
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:05,810
to explain this to my wife?

724
00:36:05,850 --> 00:36:07,130
She needs to answer your mother tonight.

725
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:08,400
Xiao'er,

726
00:36:08,680 --> 00:36:09,810
just tell her

727
00:36:09,810 --> 00:36:10,570
to tell my mother

728
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:11,610
to come to me.

729
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:13,010
Tell her not to bother
my sister-in-law anymore.

730
00:36:13,370 --> 00:36:14,010
All right.

731
00:36:14,850 --> 00:36:15,960
You deal with your mother yourself.

732
00:36:17,130 --> 00:36:17,440
Okay.

733
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:17,880
I've been here for so long,

734
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:18,960
but I haven't even gotten a drink.

735
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:24,810
Where's your liquor?

736
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:27,290
Liquor? My stomach is sensitive,
so I gave them all away.

737
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:28,810
No alcohol?

738
00:36:28,810 --> 00:36:29,770
Drink some water.

739
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:33,130
Oh, right.

740
00:36:33,770 --> 00:36:34,680
Liuzheng is back.

741
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,570
Any chance of you two
getting back together?

742
00:36:38,160 --> 00:36:38,850
No.

743
00:36:39,850 --> 00:36:40,570
Xiao'er,

744
00:36:40,570 --> 00:36:42,010
I have an operation tomorrow.

745
00:36:42,010 --> 00:36:43,290
Go home.

746
00:36:43,290 --> 00:36:44,200
We can talk some other day.

747
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:44,850
I still have one sip left.

748
00:36:44,850 --> 00:36:45,880
Don't waste water.

749
00:36:48,370 --> 00:36:50,090
Call me before you come next time.

750
00:36:50,370 --> 00:36:50,880
You...

751
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:11,330
Xiao'er cares about you a lot.

752
00:37:13,810 --> 00:37:14,920
Xiao'er is great,

753
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,240
but he's just
a little too enthusiastic sometimes.

754
00:37:17,530 --> 00:37:19,050
He found you

755
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,240
over a dozen ladies
from all professions.

756
00:37:21,240 --> 00:37:22,530
Can you handle all of them?

757
00:37:24,770 --> 00:37:25,610
Well.

758
00:37:26,010 --> 00:37:27,770
We were speaking so softly.

759
00:37:27,770 --> 00:37:28,880
Yet, you still heard us?

760
00:37:29,610 --> 00:37:30,850
I heard everything.

761
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:32,570
I'm leaving.

762
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,050
Don't go yet.

763
00:37:35,050 --> 00:37:36,610
He might still be downstairs.

764
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,200
You have nothing to do. Why don't you...

765
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,090
I'm not doing the dishes.

766
00:37:42,050 --> 00:37:42,640
No.

767
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:44,330
I meant to say
maybe you could rest here for a bit.

768
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:46,850
That's more like it.

769
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:54,790
(Beiya Hospital)

770
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:58,400
Besides the dozens Xiao'er

771
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,290
introduced him to,

772
00:38:00,770 --> 00:38:04,440
I introduced him
to a bunch of other women too.

773
00:38:05,330 --> 00:38:06,770
I was worried you would be upset,

774
00:38:06,770 --> 00:38:08,400
so I didn't tell you.

775
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:12,770
Also,

776
00:38:12,810 --> 00:38:14,480
I heard things aren't going well

777
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:15,570
between him and Huang Qian,

778
00:38:15,810 --> 00:38:17,240
whom he wanted me to introduce him to.

779
00:38:20,770 --> 00:38:21,810
Why?

780
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:22,810
Well.

781
00:38:23,370 --> 00:38:25,680
Ning Zhiqian is too picky.

782
00:38:26,090 --> 00:38:27,370
She's a nice lady,

783
00:38:27,370 --> 00:38:29,200
but he kept nitpicking her.

784
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,920
This time, he complained

785
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:33,480
that she talked too much.

786
00:38:35,130 --> 00:38:36,920
I mean, he's such a stoic guy.

787
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,770
He needs someone
that's more extroverted and lively

788
00:38:38,810 --> 00:38:39,720
to match him, right?

789
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:41,160
Doesn't that make sense?

790
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:42,440
Yes.

791
00:38:48,090 --> 00:38:49,480
My aunt sent me a message.

792
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:52,010
She says she wants to introduce me
to a university lecturer.

793
00:38:52,370 --> 00:38:54,050
A university lecturer sounds good.

794
00:38:54,290 --> 00:38:55,570
Sounds like a great candidate.

795
00:38:55,570 --> 00:38:56,090
Are you going to meet him?

796
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:57,570
Of course. Why not?

797
00:38:59,090 --> 00:38:59,960
Liuzheng,

798
00:39:00,770 --> 00:39:01,960
I support you.

799
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:04,330
You need to take the first step

800
00:39:04,570 --> 00:39:06,570
to enter a new horizon.

801
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:08,010
Zhao Cong, you go back first.

802
00:39:08,050 --> 00:39:09,130
- Okay.
- I need to discuss with Dr. Ruan

803
00:39:09,130 --> 00:39:10,290
the surgery plan for this afternoon.

804
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:10,770
All right.

805
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:12,880
But when you look around,

806
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:15,610
you'll find the scenery
ever so familiar.

807
00:39:18,090 --> 00:39:18,960
What are you guys talking about?

808
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:21,850
Have you set a date for your blind date?

809
00:39:22,090 --> 00:39:23,200
Yes. It's this Saturday.

810
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,530
Aren't you seeing another on Sunday?

811
00:39:26,610 --> 00:39:27,770
Do you have enough clothes?

812
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,770
Why don't I

813
00:39:28,770 --> 00:39:29,850
go shopping with you after work today?

814
00:39:30,010 --> 00:39:31,330
Let's take it one at a time.

815
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:35,290
I'm needed back at my department.
I have to go.

816
00:39:35,290 --> 00:39:36,050
Go get busy.

817
00:39:36,050 --> 00:39:37,440
Be sure to make well the arrangements.

818
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:39,050
Stagger the dates.

819
00:39:43,240 --> 00:39:44,570
I see you have a busy weekend coming up.

820
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:47,240
What? You can do it, but I can't?

821
00:39:49,130 --> 00:39:50,530
Do whatever you want.

822
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,850
I'm just thinking about how
I'm going to explain this to Ning Xiang.

823
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,680
Explain what?

824
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:56,960
Ning Xiang still thinks
you're his biological mother.

825
00:39:57,090 --> 00:39:59,130
If you find him a stepfather...

826
00:39:59,130 --> 00:40:01,330
You worry too much.

827
00:40:01,530 --> 00:40:02,680
Drink your yoghurt.

828
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,720
You wouldn't know
since you don't have any kids.

829
00:40:05,810 --> 00:40:06,680
A parent always worries.

830
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:16,400
What's taking her so long?

831
00:40:19,010 --> 00:40:20,050
What's going on...

832
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,570
Are you going to the blind date
dressing like that?

833
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:27,530
No.

834
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:29,330
This looks too dull.

835
00:40:29,330 --> 00:40:30,050
I think it looks fine.

836
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:31,850
Wait right here.

837
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:41,200
I bought this just for you.

838
00:40:45,610 --> 00:40:47,160
Doesn't it look good?

839
00:40:48,610 --> 00:40:49,770
This is too much.

840
00:40:49,770 --> 00:40:52,200
It looks like a soaked snow fungus.

841
00:40:53,090 --> 00:40:54,570
The pink is lovely.

842
00:40:54,570 --> 00:40:55,680
You have fair skin.

